Package cat.species

Class Lynx

java.lang.Object
cat.BigCat
cat.species.Lynx
public class Lynx
extends BigCat
This is a concrete sub class of a concrete super class BigCat and will only have access to the public and protected variables of this class which are the public variable BigCat.name and the protected variable BigCat.hasFur. As this class is in a different package to BigCat, it will not be able to access the package level variables To see video tutorial for this section of code Video tutorial For all 177 videos, which cover all the topics in this course go to Complete Course Video Tutorial
